+." $NetBSD$
+.Dd March 13, 2026
+.Dt CELLMGR 8
+.Os
+.Sh NAME
+.Nm cellmgr
+.Nd unified declarative and runtime control plane for cells, overlays, and volumes
+.Sh SYNOPSIS
+.Nm
+.Cm system
+.Cm bootstrap
+.Op Cm --xbase
+.Nm
+.Cm ipc
+.Cm serve
+.Op Cm --stdio
+.Nm
+.Cm cell
+.Cm list
+.Op Cm --view Ar merged|desired|runtime
+.Op Fl o Ar fields
+.Op Fl T
+.Op Fl H
+.Nm
